“Ensuring enough quality sleep should be a student’s ‘secret weapon’ to combat stress, exhaustion and anxiety,” he added.
Raymond So, a 19-year-old chemical and physical biology student from California, helped Professor Czeisler create the course after attending one of his classes last year, in his first year at Harvard.
